**नास्तिक हूं आस्तिक है जावै । जब स्वामी चेतक दिखलावै ॥**

Word-by-word breakdown:

**नास्तिक** (nastika) - "non-believer" or "atheist"
**हूं** (hun) - "being" or "who is"
**आस्तिक** (astika) - "believer" or "theist"
**है** (hai) - "becomes"
**जावै** (jaavai) - "goes" or "becomes"

**जब** (jaba) - "when"
**स्वामी** (swami) - "Lord" or "master"
**चेतक** (chetaka) - "warning" or "awakening sign"
**दिखलावै** (dikhalaavai) - "shows" or "reveals"

Translation: "A non-believer becomes a believer when the Lord shows them an awakening sign or warning."